name: Juwita Suwito - Faith Upon Favor (Malaysia Edition)
description:
A compilation album in celebration of Eagles Communications' 45th Anniversary.

"Somehow, when Peter, John and Michael approached me about this project, something inside just clicked. As I started selecting some of the songs that we had recorded and released over the last ten years, I realized that they tell of my journey of faith on the wings of God's abounding favor and grace."
- Juwita Suwito

"We are thankful to Juwita Suwito for producing and performing in this specially commissioned music album in celebrating Eagles' 45th Anniversary. Her talent shines through in every song. Her heart for the Lord pulsates throughout this album!"
- Michael Tan, Executive Vice-President, Eagles Communications

Track Listing:
01. Leading Change
02. What's On Your Mind?
03. Walking Again
04. Safe
05. Take Me On - featuring Patrick Leong
06. For Real
07. You in Me
08. Fairest Lord Jesus
09. Stand
10. Closing Prayer
